die in the Lord; thou must liue the
life of the righteous, if thou wouldest
wish to die the death of the
righteous, and thy last end to bee

like theirs. All the holy Patriarks,
Prophets, Saints, and Martyrs of
God, haue trode this narrow way,
before they obtayned the recompence
of their reward, vnto which
they had respect: if therefore thou
haue any respect vnto the same,
and by hope looke for that, which
they fully now possesse, follow and
insist in their footsteps; if thou
