to vs present remedie, not
to restore the bodie to a kind of
health, that it may liue a miserable
momentaneall life, for a while, but
to restore the soule to perfect and
true health, that it may liue a blessed,
ioyfull, and eternall ioy in heauen,
with God and his blessed Angels,
